claim.claim-text:
7. An image processing device comprising:
a pixel;
a ramp voltage generator for outputting a ramp signal;
a differential amplifier including a tail and amplifying a difference between a pixel signal output by the pixel and the ramp signal;
a current mirror connected between output terminals of the differential amplifier and a power line receiving a supply voltage; and
a switching circuit for connecting and disconnecting a line receiving a voltage to and from the tail in response to a switching signal.
